00047 void FusionCdfFileTest::testQCObjects(affxcdf::CCDFFileData &gcosCdf, affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFData &fusionCdf)
00048 {
00049         affxcdf::CCDFFileHeader &gcosHeader = gcosCdf.GetHeader();
00050         affxcdf::CCDFQCProbeSetInformation gcosSet;
00051         affxcdf::CCDFQCProbeInformation gcosCel;
00052 
00053         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFFileHeader &fusionHeader = fusionCdf.GetHeader();
00054         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFQCProbeSetInformation fusionSet;
00055         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFQCProbeInformation fusionCel;
00056 
00057         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetHeader().GetCols() == fusionCdf.GetHeader().GetCols());
00058         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetHeader().GetRows() == fusionCdf.GetHeader().GetRows());
00059         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetHeader().GetNumQCProbeSets() == fusionCdf.GetHeader().GetNumQCProbeSets());
00060         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetChipType() == fusionCdf.GetChipType());
00061         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetFileName() == fusionCdf.GetFileName());
00062 
00063         int nps = gcosCdf.GetHeader().GetNumQCProbeSets();
00064         for (int ips=0; ips<nps; ips++)
00065         {
00066                 gcosCdf.GetQCProbeSetInformation(ips, gcosSet);
00067                 fusionCdf.GetQCProbeSetInformation(ips, fusionSet);
00068 
00069                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetQCProbeSetType() == fusionSet.GetQCProbeSetType());
00070                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumCells() == fusionSet.GetNumCells());
00071 
00072                 int nc = gcosSet.GetNumCells();
00073                 for (int ic=0; ic<nc; ic++)
00074                 {
00075                         gcosSet.GetProbeInformation(ic, gcosCel);
00076                         fusionSet.GetProbeInformation(ic, fusionCel);
00077 
00078                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetX() == fusionCel.GetX());
00079                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetY() == fusionCel.GetY());
00080                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetPLen() == fusionCel.GetPLen());
00081                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.IsPerfectMatchProbe() == fusionCel.IsPerfectMatchProbe());
00082                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.IsBackgroundProbe() == fusionCel.IsBackgroundProbe());
00083                 }
00084         }
00085 }
00086 void FusionCdfFileTest::testRegObjects(affxcdf::CCDFFileData &gcosCdf, affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFData &fusionCdf)
00087 {
00088         affxcdf::CCDFFileHeader &gcosHeader = gcosCdf.GetHeader();
00089         affxcdf::CCDFProbeSetInformation gcosSet;
00090         affxcdf::CCDFProbeGroupInformation gcosGroup;
00091         affxcdf::CCDFProbeInformation gcosCel;
00092 
00093         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFFileHeader &fusionHeader = fusionCdf.GetHeader();
00094         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFProbeSetInformation fusionSet;
00095         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFProbeGroupInformation fusionGroup;
00096         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFProbeInformation fusionCel;
00097 
00098         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetCols() == fusionHeader.GetCols());
00099         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetRows() == fusionHeader.GetRows());
00100         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetNumProbeSets() == fusionHeader.GetNumProbeSets());
00101         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetNumQCProbeSets() == fusionHeader.GetNumQCProbeSets());
00102         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetReference() == fusionHeader.GetReference());
00103         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetChipType() == fusionCdf.GetChipType());
00104         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetFileName() == fusionCdf.GetFileName());
00105 
00106         int nps = gcosHeader.GetNumProbeSets();
00107         for (int ips=0; ips<nps; ips++)
00108         {
00109                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetProbeSetName(ips) == fusionCdf.GetProbeSetName(ips));
00110                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetProbeSetType(ips) == fusionCdf.GetProbeSetType(ips));
00111         }
00112 
00113         for (int ips=0; ips<nps; ips++)
00114         {
00115                 gcosCdf.GetProbeSetInformation(ips, gcosSet);
00116                 fusionCdf.GetProbeSetInformation(ips, fusionSet);
00117 
00118                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumLists() == fusionSet.GetNumLists());
00119                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumGroups() == fusionSet.GetNumGroups());
00120                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumCells() == fusionSet.GetNumCells());
00121                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumCellsPerList() == fusionSet.GetNumCellsPerList());
00122                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetProbeSetNumber() == fusionSet.GetProbeSetNumber());
00123                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetProbeSetType() == fusionSet.GetProbeSetType());
00124                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetDirection() == fusionSet.GetDirection());
00125 
00126                 int ng = gcosSet.GetNumGroups();
00127                 for (int ig=0; ig<ng; ig++)
00128                 {
00129                         gcosSet.GetGroupInformation(ig, gcosGroup);
00130                         fusionSet.GetGroupInformation(ig, fusionGroup);
00131 
00132                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetDirection() == fusionGroup.GetDirection());
00133                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetNumLists() == fusionGroup.GetNumLists());
00134                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetNumCells() == fusionGroup.GetNumCells());
00135                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetNumCellsPerList() == fusionGroup.GetNumCellsPerList());
00136                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetStart() == fusionGroup.GetStart());
00137                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetStop() == fusionGroup.GetStop());
00138                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetName() == fusionGroup.GetName());
00139                         
00140                         int nc=gcosGroup.GetNumCells();
00141                         for (int ic=0; ic<nc; ic++)
00142                         {
00143                                 gcosGroup.GetCell(ic, gcosCel);
00144                                 fusionGroup.GetCell(ic, fusionCel);
00145 
00146                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetX() == fusionCel.GetX());
00147                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetY() == fusionCel.GetY());
00148                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetListIndex() == fusionCel.GetListIndex());
00149                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetExpos() == fusionCel.GetExpos());
00150                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetPBase() == fusionCel.GetPBase());
00151                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetTBase() == fusionCel.GetTBase());
00152                         }
00153                 }
00154         }
